Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:26.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ame agari no sora wo aogu tabi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:31.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:31.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:37.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:37.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.19,0:00:44.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:44.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:47.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:53.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:58.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:58.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:04.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:04.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:09.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:09.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:11.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:15.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:15.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:20.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:26.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:26.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:31.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:31.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:36.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:42.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:42.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:47.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:47.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:52.43,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:52.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:55.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:55.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:01:57.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:01.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:01.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.02,0:02:06.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:06.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:11.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:11.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:17.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:17.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:25.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is rushing to Navy HQ\N to rescue his brother, Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is waiting to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'll appear from \Nwhere we least expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we got the wrong lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a shadow in the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got all their ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:04:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...coated and approached from underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Beginning of the War! \NAce and Whitebeard's Past!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There are 3 more Whitebeard Pirates ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've infiltrated the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...1st division commander--Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14 commanders--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile, Sengoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell me that my beloved son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that \Nwe let them get this close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through the gate but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what I'm concerned about is \Nwhether your father is here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that Dragon \Nwould let them kill his own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my dad and Ace's are not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad is Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ace's dad is Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a great father but he never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd get mad every time I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He cracked the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that explosion coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! The water surface is too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A seaquake! He's distorting the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other side, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. See you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a lot stronger when \NI leave here in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show them how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! He became a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pirate ship! I never seen their flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pirate whose become  \Nvery powerful rapidly recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"D?" Where is he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't quite figure that out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even as a rookie,\N he has the power of Logia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a dashing young man in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He refused the offer to join the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have they been at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Red-Haired" Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spade Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The infamous super rookie  \Ncame to say hello to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was always talking \Nabout you as his lifesaver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Luffy's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that he had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, I'm glad to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me all about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's still talking about \Nbecoming the King of the pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's his favorite phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll become the next King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll let the whole world\N know the power I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How'll you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By beating the strongest man in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Whitebeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, big guy, I wanna see the \Nguy who goes by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot introduce a sharp \Nyoung man like you to the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, that's Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Warlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd gain prestige if I beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not on the crew of the Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe him, so I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 5 days since they started fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you wants to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you people single-handedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ace, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? \NAre you backing away after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let my crew get way. Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You snot-nosed brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cheeky you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the guy who contended \Nfor supremacy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still wanna run wild,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run as wild as you want \Non the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 4th division commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Thatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna join us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're grumpy when you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you wanna know what \Nhappened after you passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your crew came to get you back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we beat the hell out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're not dead. \NThey're on this ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to put \Nme in cuffs or shackles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shackles? We don't need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:16:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, he fell overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been at it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How gutsy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be more than 100 times now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you people call him Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:17:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he calls us "sons."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are all hated by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's just a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna keep doing this \Nafter your life has been saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got to make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not capable of killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either get off of this ship\N and start over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or stay here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wear the Whitebeard logo on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made Doma and his crew \Nsurrender  by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to command 2nd division?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a vacant post for a \Nlong time. If you took it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Nobody would complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the originals, right? \NDon't you mind it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no such ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it for us! Commander Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, you got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your character is nothing like Roger's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was your enemy, right? \NDon't you wanna kick me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that it's important \Nbut it's such a small matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who your father is, \Nwe are all children of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace will be our 2nd division commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a star, don't look dazed. Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the food's not leaving so don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the star of this banquet so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He falls asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard got a powerful newbie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he's insanely strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd division come to cover us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thatch, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bounty will rise again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, I found something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it a devil fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what fruit it is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Ace, just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops said that this is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go after Teech!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! I am his commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do anything about it, \NThatch's spirit can't rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. This is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed his crewmate and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had been beholden to you for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then he threw dirt in your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And above all, he disgraced my father's name
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Come back, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What caused that quake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ignored your advice and took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you just give up on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who caused all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who told you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the cast has assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard's tremendous \Npower brings a huge tsunami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that threatens to swallow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the brave men of Marineford, as \Nwell as the peace and justice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle crossing generations begins at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Force That Could Destroy the World! \NThe Power of the Tremor-Tremor Fruit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
